357
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:27,450
What are you doing here?

358
00:18:29,260 --> 00:18:30,460
It's you three again.

359
00:18:31,060 --> 00:18:32,920
What are you sneaking around for?

360
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:33,740
Director Hu,

361
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:35,500
