375
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:06,950
It feels so good!

376
00:19:07,150 --> 00:19:09,410
I haven't had anything this good in ages!

377
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,060
We get up at the crack of dawn.

378
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:11,590
Yeah.

379
00:19:11,630 --> 00:19:13,060
And we have evening self-study every day!

380
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:13,630
Yeah.

381
00:19:13,670 --> 00:19:15,110
