398
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:42,830
Like me!

399
00:19:42,830 --> 00:19:43,540
Like me!

400
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:44,220
Like me!

401
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:45,120
And me!

402
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:46,390
