We're only asking to be

567
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:53,440
treated equally, regardless of our grades.

568
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:58,910
Tong Xiaole, if you put it that way...

569
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:06,350
I think what Tong Xiaole said
is worth reflecting on.

570
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,190
Our education

571
00:29:07,460 --> 00:29:09,840
should indeed be more humanized.

572
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:18,540
After careful reflection,
the School Committee

573
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:21,190
acknowledges
that this decision was flawed.

574
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:22,500
Any reform

575
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:23,190
must be grounded

576
00:29:23,190 --> 00:29:26,590
in respect for students
and an understanding of their needs.

577
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:29,760
Therefore, we have decided to
revoke the new rules,

578
00:29:29,870 --> 00:29:31,070
restore the old ones,

579
00:29:31,540 --> 00:29:33,340
cancel the Experimental Class,

580
00:29:34,150 --> 00:29:36,010
and ensure that all classes

581
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:39,130
receive equal attention and resources.

582
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,670
We will also make sure

583
00:29:41,670 --> 00:29:43,000
every student is heard.

584
00:29:43,760 --> 00:29:45,260
So the perks of the Experimental Class
are gone!

585
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,460
What am I supposed to do?

586
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,700
Shut up!

587
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:48,950
Get out of here!

588
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:50,980
An inclusive learning atmosphere.
